no1cOZZhD1RChRPI1IH5FmiVIm03.name: Rolex GMT-Master II "Pepsi" 126710BLRO – Oystersteel Jubilee Bracelet
no1cOZZhD1RChRPI1IH5FmiVIm03.description: The Rolex GMT-Master II 126710BLRO, affectionately known as the "Pepsi," is one of the most iconic luxury travel watches ever created. Crafted in robust Oystersteel, it features a striking bi-color red and blue Cerachrom bezel that represents day and night. Equipped with the state-of-the-art Calibre 3285 automatic movement, this timepiece offers dual time zone functionality, a 70-hour power reserve, and superb chronometric precision. Its elegant Jubilee bracelet ensures comfort and timeless style, making it the ultimate companion for world travelers and watch enthusiasts alike.
